WEBVTT

WEBVTT

00:09.273 --> 00:12.702
(Lee Jae In. Kim Woo Seok. Choi Ye Bin)

00:13.303 --> 00:16.972
(Cha Woo Min. An Ji Ho. Jung So Ri)

00:17.573 --> 00:21.042
(Scriptwriter: Kang Min Ji)

00:21.582 --> 00:25.113
(Director: Im Dae Woong)

00:27.122 --> 00:31.393
(Night Has Come)

00:31.493 --> 00:33.423
(All people. organizations. locations. and incidents...)

00:33.423 --> 00:34.762
(in this drama are fictitious.)

01:43.932 --> 01:48.132
(Night has come.)

03:41.712 --> 03:42.983
("Murder of a White Butterfly")

03:50.723 --> 03:53.323
(Yooil High School)

03:56.432 --> 03:58.032
- It's not me. - Hey. guys.

03:58.133 --> 04:00.562
- It's really not me. - Stop lying. It's you.

04:00.562 --> 04:02.872
- Why won't you listen to me? Gosh. - Seriously. She has to be it.

04:02.872 --> 04:04.073
- Are you for real? - Hey.

04:04.073 --> 04:06.302
- I told you it wasn't me! - It has to be you. Come on.

04:07.443 --> 04:09.242
- Just think. If I were the Mafia. - I know it's you!

04:09.242 --> 04:10.312
- why did I help you... - Come on.

04:10.312 --> 04:11.372
when you were suspected?

04:11.372 --> 04:13.613
- It's not that! I... - Seriously. Heo Yul is the Mafia.

04:13.613 --> 04:15.343
- It's you. - All right.

04:15.343 --> 04:18.052
- Okay. All right. - Right.

04:21.783 --> 04:24.523
The innocent citizens have lost. and the Mafia has won!

04:24.523 --> 04:25.992
- Yes! - What?

04:26.293 --> 04:28.322
- I told you I was a citizen! - Gosh.

04:28.322 --> 04:29.793
You just won't believe me.

04:29.793 --> 04:31.093
- You carried this game. - You said you were a citizen!

04:31.093 --> 04:33.333
- I told you he was the Mafia. - It was you?

04:33.333 --> 04:35.802
- Let's play another one. - Okay. Let's play again.

04:35.802 --> 04:37.233
- They're so loud. - Hurry.

04:37.432 --> 04:39.103
Starting with the next game...

04:39.103 --> 04:40.302
- I have my eyes on you now. - Losers going to buy...

04:40.302 --> 04:41.543
snacks this time. Are you in?

04:41.673 --> 04:42.812
- I'm in! - Darn it.

04:42.812 --> 04:43.973
- Hey. - Let's start now.

04:43.973 --> 04:45.242
Tell them to shut their mouths.

04:45.242 --> 04:47.382
Heo Yul will be the first one I kill in the next round.

04:48.583 --> 04:49.812
- Hey! - Hurry.

04:50.012 --> 04:51.512
Kyung Jun is sleeping right now.

04:52.283 --> 04:53.423
You're so loud.

04:59.762 --> 05:01.163
Those jerks.

05:01.923 --> 05:03.562
Hey. stop it.

05:12.403 --> 05:13.473
Hey. Na Hee.

05:14.572 --> 05:16.473
Don't talk to Na Hee.

05:19.442 --> 05:20.812
You'll get chewed out again.

05:20.812 --> 05:23.483
Hey. Switch. Come on. do it.

05:23.483 --> 05:25.382
He likes her. Switch seats with him.

05:25.382 --> 05:27.223
Hey. Doesn't he look gorgeous or what?

05:27.523 --> 05:28.552
This belongs in a magazine. doesn't it?

05:29.622 --> 05:31.093
How can he look this gorgeous?

05:31.093 --> 05:33.163
I'll tell Jun Hee tomorrow that you secretly took a photo of him.

05:33.963 --> 05:36.793
Could you please do that? Let me seduce him while we're at it.

05:36.863 --> 05:38.692
You've been saying that since last year. When will you do it?

05:38.692 --> 05:40.062
- You can do it now. - I'll do it soon.

05:40.603 --> 05:42.603
- Jun Hee. - Stop it.

05:45.872 --> 05:46.973
Look at this.

05:51.242 --> 05:53.913
Why don't you just sit next to him if you're going to stare at him?

05:55.642 --> 05:56.952
I wasn't staring.

06:17.002 --> 06:18.572
(Game Development Contest)

07:05.413 --> 07:07.983
(Yooil High School. Class 2-3)

07:08.023 --> 07:09.083
Hello. Ms. Kim.

07:09.083 --> 07:11.423
- Did you find it? - What?

07:11.593 --> 07:13.723
- Right now. I'm... - Hello.

07:13.723 --> 07:15.622
- What did you say? - I can't...

07:15.622 --> 07:18.663
- Hello? No. - Can you not hear me?

07:18.932 --> 07:21.262
- I can't hear you well. Hello? - Should we go?

07:21.762 --> 07:22.802
- Sure. - What?

07:22.802 --> 07:25.103
- Hey. Hyun Ho. Can you help me? - Only our class arrived?

07:44.892 --> 07:45.892
Give me that.

07:48.262 --> 07:49.262
I...

07:59.673 --> 08:00.702
Hey.

08:01.302 --> 08:03.843
Have we been here before? Why do I feel like I've been here?

08:04.413 --> 08:06.182
Retreat centers are all the same.

08:17.653 --> 08:18.723
Hey. Lee Yoon Seo.

08:20.492 --> 08:22.622
- I'm going inside. - Okay.

08:26.632 --> 08:28.433
- Yoon Seo. - What?

08:28.433 --> 08:30.073
What are you doing? Let's go inside.

08:31.032 --> 08:32.032
Okay.

08:38.772 --> 08:40.782
Darn it. This is so annoying.

08:54.863 --> 08:55.992
(Scan the QR code to connect to Wi-Fi...)

08:55.992 --> 08:57.193
(and to install the retreat center's facility app.)

09:01.662 --> 09:03.132
Still haven't decided on your birthday present?

09:04.372 --> 09:05.502
You'd better tell me by today.

09:05.502 --> 09:07.142
I won't buy you a thing if you tell me past midnight.

09:07.203 --> 09:08.973
Good grief. You're so petty.

09:10.512 --> 09:11.912
But I still haven't decided yet.

09:13.742 --> 09:14.782
A mystery novel?

09:15.142 --> 09:17.083
- Yes. That. - Okay.

09:18.053 --> 09:19.353
Gosh. You and mystery novels.

09:20.652 --> 09:24.022
My phone isn't getting any reception. Is this normal here?

09:24.693 --> 09:27.162
Excuse me. Can I make a phone call?

09:27.563 --> 09:29.063
The phone line is down now.

09:29.693 --> 09:32.132
What should I do? Should I go to them?

09:51.752 --> 09:55.522
(Welcome to Muryeong Retreat Center.)

10:41.902 --> 10:42.902
Oh. my.

10:45.032 --> 10:47.803
Look at So Mi flirting. Seriously.

10:58.752 --> 11:00.053
- Hey. - What?

11:00.922 --> 11:03.093
Stop staring at him. You're making it obvious.

11:04.193 --> 11:05.353
I wasn't staring at him.

11:06.522 --> 11:07.593
As if.

11:08.823 --> 11:11.032
(Guide Map of Muryeong Retreat Center)

11:12.032 --> 11:13.303
This is so lame.

11:13.463 --> 11:15.433
I can make this in a day.

11:16.032 --> 11:17.103
What are you talking about?

11:18.333 --> 11:19.402
You didn't scan the QR code?

11:19.772 --> 11:21.002
It was installed automatically.

11:22.642 --> 11:24.042
Give me your phone. I'll do it for you.

11:24.113 --> 11:25.343
What? No.

11:26.282 --> 11:27.542
I can read this.

11:28.213 --> 11:29.953
Do you want to carry that with you for two whole days?

11:34.353 --> 11:35.752
- Class President. - Yes.

11:38.992 --> 11:40.863
I need to go and pick up the students in other classes.

11:40.863 --> 11:42.392
Don't do anything. Just stay in your rooms.

11:43.333 --> 11:45.292
Keep an eye on your class. so they don't cause trouble.

11:45.292 --> 11:46.603
Okay. I will.

11:46.762 --> 11:48.433
- Help him. Vice President. - Okay.

11:48.532 --> 11:50.372
Once I come back. we have to take a group picture at night.

11:50.573 --> 11:52.002
Tell them to keep their uniforms on.

11:52.603 --> 11:53.703
- Okay. - I'm leaving now.

11:54.073 --> 11:55.103
Okay.

11:56.372 --> 11:58.272
What's going on? Why is he so busy?

12:02.843 --> 12:05.012
Wi-Fi isn't working here. This place is awful.

12:07.953 --> 12:09.992
But why are we taking a group picture at night?

12:11.593 --> 12:12.593
Who knows?

12:16.833 --> 12:18.392
I'm not getting any signals at all.

12:24.433 --> 12:26.132
(The phone is out of the service area.)

12:37.012 --> 12:39.583
Hey. He's filming us again.

12:43.752 --> 12:46.463
Seriously. He has high standards.

12:47.693 --> 12:50.662
He's not filming us. It's just me.

12:51.863 --> 12:53.703
What can I do? It's all my fault.

12:54.563 --> 12:56.973
Get over yourself. Seriously.

13:04.642 --> 13:06.483
Come on. What is this?

13:07.083 --> 13:08.912
- What's going on? - What is this?

13:09.382 --> 13:10.583
Hey. turn on the lights.

13:10.912 --> 13:12.382
What are you doing?

13:13.752 --> 13:16.053
- What is it? - What?

13:18.622 --> 13:20.063
What's going on?

13:23.693 --> 13:25.892
- Quit joking around. - Come on.

13:26.093 --> 13:27.563
- Are you serious? - Gosh.

13:27.563 --> 13:28.762
- Hey. - You!

13:28.863 --> 13:30.073
He's so annoying.

13:30.502 --> 13:31.772
- Come on. - Gosh.

13:31.772 --> 13:34.073
- Darn it. That lunatic. - What was that?

13:35.473 --> 13:37.073
Hey. listen carefully.

13:38.172 --> 13:39.313
Here's what I heard here.

13:39.882 --> 13:41.713
A long time ago. a high school girl killed herself here.

13:43.512 --> 13:45.382
So there are a few things you must not do here.

13:46.453 --> 13:48.553
Don't look in the mirror and turn around at midnight.

13:50.522 --> 13:52.652
And if someone grabs your ankle when you're sleeping.

13:52.892 --> 13:54.063
don't look down.

13:54.963 --> 13:56.022
If you break these rules.

13:58.063 --> 13:59.132
a ghost will pop up!

13:59.803 --> 14:02.363
- Hey! - Get lost. That crazy jerk!

14:02.563 --> 14:03.573
What?

14:03.733 --> 14:05.303
- You lunatic. - Come on.

14:05.372 --> 14:06.443
Are you scared?

14:07.343 --> 14:08.642
Stop that.

14:09.813 --> 14:11.813
- Let's go back to our room. - Okay.

14:28.563 --> 14:29.593
Hey.

14:30.992 --> 14:33.233
When can you give my money back?

14:33.733 --> 14:35.203
I need to pay the tuition at the academy.

14:37.032 --> 14:38.203
Ju Won.

14:38.933 --> 14:40.703
Don't be like that. We're friends.

14:41.402 --> 14:43.412
I told you I was going to pay you interest too.

14:44.073 --> 14:45.172
Give me some more time.

14:46.242 --> 14:48.882
- I need it by next... - Shut it! Darn you. jerk.

14:49.912 --> 14:50.912
Are you a loan shark?

14:51.252 --> 14:53.083
We're here on a retreat. Why are you asking us for money?

14:53.122 --> 14:55.683
Did you do sports betting again? Did you?

15:00.323 --> 15:02.662
Da Bum. Did you lend them money too?

15:03.563 --> 15:04.563
What?

15:07.803 --> 15:08.963
Yes.

15:10.002 --> 15:13.002
But I can wait for my money. There's no rush.

15:14.803 --> 15:15.902
How much is the total?

15:17.642 --> 15:18.772
I'll pay you back.

15:21.012 --> 15:22.042
In return.

15:23.713 --> 15:26.183
play basketball with me. Are you in?

16:00.353 --> 16:02.022
(Unable to connect to the Internet)

16:03.292 --> 16:04.892
I need to watch a special lecture on coding online.

16:06.723 --> 16:08.463
Why isn't it working?

16:09.892 --> 16:10.992
What are you doing?

16:12.563 --> 16:15.402
Gosh. You teased me for reading a book.

16:16.262 --> 16:19.843
Hey. Who studies on a school trip?

16:20.973 --> 16:23.002
Don't make it so obvious that you're first in class.

16:23.002 --> 16:25.943
That's why they tease you and call you Mensa.

16:27.083 --> 16:28.983
Mensa is the name of a society.

16:28.983 --> 16:31.382
The members of the society are called Mensans.

16:32.353 --> 16:33.422
How many times must I tell you that?

16:37.453 --> 16:39.252
(Installing)

16:44.433 --> 16:45.433
What's this?

16:47.703 --> 16:49.162
I told you I didn't need this.

16:50.473 --> 16:51.973
It wasn't me.

17:00.243 --> 17:01.283
(Welcome.)

17:01.283 --> 17:04.283
(The Mafia Game will begin now. Check your identity.)

17:07.982 --> 17:11.523
(Lee Yoon Seo. your identity is a citizen.)

17:11.652 --> 17:12.753
What's this?

17:13.892 --> 17:14.993
I'm a citizen.

17:15.793 --> 17:17.432
- What about you? - Me too.

17:18.692 --> 17:20.962
(Main Menu: Chat. Vote. Rules. Voting Status. Participants)

17:26.843 --> 17:28.573
(The participants' identities will secretly be assigned.)

17:28.573 --> 17:29.642
(The identities...)

17:29.642 --> 17:32.813
(are citizens. doctors. police officers. and the Mafia.)

17:34.982 --> 17:37.553
(A doctor can prevent a participant of choice from getting executed.)

17:37.882 --> 17:39.783
(the occupation of a selected participant.)

17:39.783 --> 17:41.682
(the identity of a selected participant.)

17:43.553 --> 17:46.922
(The participants have from 8am to midnight...)

17:47.263 --> 17:50.293
(to ferret out the Mafia through a vote.)

17:51.363 --> 17:52.593
(At midnight. the one with the most votes will be executed.)

17:52.593 --> 17:53.732
What's this?

17:55.333 --> 17:57.603
(And the executed participant's identity will be disclosed.)

18:00.142 --> 18:01.803
(After the vote at midnight.)

18:02.043 --> 18:04.972
(all the participants excluding the Mafia will go to sleep.)

18:05.942 --> 18:08.043
Ju Won. Let me give this a shot.

18:08.982 --> 18:10.013
Stand right there.

18:10.212 --> 18:11.212
Here it goes.

18:11.212 --> 18:12.482
(When the participants are asleep during the night.)

18:13.013 --> 18:17.753
(the Mafia has until 6am...)

18:17.952 --> 18:19.053
Don't move.

18:19.053 --> 18:20.093
(to execute the participant personally.)

18:24.363 --> 18:25.392
(When the participants are asleep during the night.)

18:25.392 --> 18:26.432
(the Mafia has until 6am...)

18:30.273 --> 18:31.303
Mafia?

18:31.972 --> 18:33.033
What's this about?

18:33.702 --> 18:34.843
What the heck is this?

18:40.783 --> 18:47.853
(If Team Citizens or Team Mafia...)

18:48.783 --> 18:50.793
(wipes out the other team and wins.)

18:50.793 --> 18:53.922
(the game is over.)

18:55.962 --> 18:59.162
(Citizens. doctors and police are a team.)

19:05.702 --> 19:07.172
(All participants.)

19:07.172 --> 19:10.172
(identify the Mafia. and begin to vote.)

19:10.313 --> 19:11.372
(All participants.)

19:11.372 --> 19:12.672
(identify the Mafia. and begin to vote.)

19:13.172 --> 19:15.412
(Hi. losers.)

19:15.412 --> 19:18.013
Is it my turn to step out?

19:18.652 --> 19:21.452
Hi. losers. Let's play a game.

19:21.853 --> 19:24.523
(Is Baek Eun Ha...)

19:24.523 --> 19:25.823
Is Baek Eun Ha the mafia?

19:26.222 --> 19:27.863
Look at this jerk. He's so happy.

19:28.063 --> 19:30.263
Hey. I can't stand him.

19:31.093 --> 19:32.162
Let's kill him.

19:32.162 --> 19:34.063
All votes on him? Are you in?

19:34.603 --> 19:35.632
- I'm in. - I'm in.

19:35.863 --> 19:36.972
Okay.

19:38.073 --> 19:39.803
Heo Yul is the mafia.

19:39.902 --> 19:41.472
Let's kill Heo Yul.

19:42.472 --> 19:43.543
Okay.

19:44.543 --> 19:45.672
(Do you want to vote for Heo Yul?)

19:47.313 --> 19:48.712
(Yes.)

19:50.682 --> 19:51.712
(Im Eun Chan voted for Heo Yul.)

19:51.882 --> 19:53.583
I voted by pressing the name.

19:54.553 --> 19:55.553
Really?

19:56.083 --> 19:57.593
(Do you want to vote for Heo Yul?)

19:57.692 --> 19:58.853
(Lee Yoon Seo voted for Heo Yul.)

20:02.462 --> 20:05.263
We never signed up.

20:06.162 --> 20:08.003
but how does this know our names?

20:17.543 --> 20:19.212
There's no internet connection.

20:20.682 --> 20:22.243
How are we playing this game?

20:29.783 --> 20:31.253
What? Are they still not here yet?

20:32.593 --> 20:33.962
Our teacher's gone for a while.

20:35.222 --> 20:37.162
Do you think they are all right?

20:38.033 --> 20:39.333
What if they got into an accident?

20:40.863 --> 20:41.962
Jun Hee.

20:42.462 --> 20:43.972
Do you know when our teacher will be back?

20:44.702 --> 20:46.432
No. I couldn't reach him.

20:47.303 --> 20:48.372
Do you get receptions?

20:48.743 --> 20:50.142
No.

20:50.872 --> 20:52.172
What about the staff?

20:52.642 --> 20:54.982
I think they all left with him. There's no one.

20:55.343 --> 20:57.482
What? What do we do?

20:58.313 --> 20:59.452
How long do we have to wait?

21:00.482 --> 21:03.382
There must be a phone in the office. Let's go check.

21:04.452 --> 21:05.452
Sure.

21:15.462 --> 21:17.372
(Iced coffee)

21:17.503 --> 21:18.533
It's out.

21:22.603 --> 21:24.073
This coffee is new.

21:25.013 --> 21:26.712
Are you sure you saw nobody?

21:27.442 --> 21:29.412
Yes. I didn't see anyone.

21:34.382 --> 21:35.422
Hello?

21:39.353 --> 21:40.462
It's disconnected.

21:40.863 --> 21:43.833
Try 112 or 119.

21:43.833 --> 21:44.892
Okay.

21:57.372 --> 21:58.672
(Kim So Mi)

21:58.672 --> 22:01.113
Lee Yoon Seo. Come to the swimming pool in the other building now.

22:01.113 --> 22:02.182
It's urgent.

22:02.313 --> 22:03.482
Do you know what's going on?

22:04.053 --> 22:05.283
Well...

22:06.083 --> 22:07.622
We're all taking turns to record an interview...

22:07.622 --> 22:10.392
to play during the event tomorrow.

22:10.622 --> 22:12.053
How can we have an interview in this situation?

22:14.692 --> 22:16.462
- Let's go. - Okay.

22:28.603 --> 22:29.642
Ju Won.

22:31.872 --> 22:32.912
Where are you going?

22:33.513 --> 22:36.212
Oh. well...

22:36.682 --> 22:39.013
Other kids wanted to see me.

22:40.422 --> 22:42.182
Let me talk to him for a second.

22:43.853 --> 22:44.853
But...

22:45.323 --> 22:46.793
- Let's go. - But...

22:48.593 --> 22:49.823
It's okay. Come on.

22:58.932 --> 22:59.972
It's my turn.

23:04.043 --> 23:05.843
Hey...

23:06.243 --> 23:08.283
- Yes! - Yes!

23:09.243 --> 23:10.283
Hey.

23:11.652 --> 23:12.712
What are you doing?

23:14.452 --> 23:16.482
- Jin Da Bum. get up. - What?

23:16.652 --> 23:17.922
Get up now.

23:21.922 --> 23:22.922
Goodness.

23:25.192 --> 23:26.962
- Kyung Jun. - Yes?

23:27.863 --> 23:29.363
Don't you think your joke crossed the line?

23:31.172 --> 23:32.172
My joke?

23:35.743 --> 23:37.113
But I couldn't be more serious right now.

23:40.942 --> 23:43.113
Da Bum said he'd help us prepare for the event tomorrow.

23:44.652 --> 23:45.813
Can I take him with me?

23:46.253 --> 23:48.152
- I'm taking him. - But I...

23:49.382 --> 23:51.392
I'm okay.

23:53.692 --> 23:54.793
He said he's okay.

23:57.732 --> 24:00.232
Gosh. that prick.

24:02.462 --> 24:05.033
You think you're so handsome? Stop getting on my nerves.

24:07.942 --> 24:10.043
Darn it. Who was that?

24:10.743 --> 24:13.513
Seung Bin. you got so big.

24:14.543 --> 24:15.682
Have you been working out?

24:16.613 --> 24:19.553
Jang Hyun Ho. you jerk.

24:21.482 --> 24:24.422
Why are you causing a ruckus here?

24:29.523 --> 24:30.662
To exercise.

24:31.993 --> 24:34.303
What? You got a problem?

24:43.843 --> 24:45.773
You couldn't even become national athletes.

24:45.773 --> 24:48.243
Fine. Exercise all you want.

24:48.642 --> 24:50.513
(Jang Hyun Ho)

24:50.952 --> 24:53.613
- Let's go. - That jerk.

24:59.993 --> 25:01.622
Those jerks...

25:01.622 --> 25:03.263
Stop.

25:05.132 --> 25:06.162
Don't do it.

25:10.902 --> 25:11.902
Are you okay?

25:16.073 --> 25:17.073
Hide.

25:18.743 --> 25:20.382
Hey. you're here. Why don't you go in?

25:20.783 --> 25:23.343
Yoon Seo. you should go first.

25:23.682 --> 25:24.682
Okay.

25:27.152 --> 25:29.222
They'll start recording when Yoon Seo enters.

25:29.452 --> 25:31.053
We should wait.

25:31.622 --> 25:32.922
Why put so much effort?

25:53.142 --> 25:54.182
- Hey. - Oh. my gosh.

25:54.182 --> 25:55.712
Surprise!

25:55.982 --> 25:58.712
- Happy birthday to you - Happy birthday to you

25:58.712 --> 26:01.053
- Happy birthday to you - Happy birthday to you

26:01.053 --> 26:03.753
- Dear Yoon Seo - Dear Yoon Seo

26:03.753 --> 26:05.993
- Happy birthday to you - Happy birthday to you

26:07.122 --> 26:08.692
Imagine this is a candle and blow it out.

26:11.962 --> 26:13.493
Why are you doing this?

26:13.962 --> 26:15.303
You never talked to her before.

26:16.962 --> 26:18.172
Thank you.

26:19.033 --> 26:20.232
You're welcome.

26:20.702 --> 26:22.372
This is what friends are for.

26:23.343 --> 26:24.472
I even got you a gift.

26:26.472 --> 26:27.613
Birthday noogies!

26:30.753 --> 26:32.513
- Hey. - Are you ready?

26:32.513 --> 26:34.053
Throw her or not?

26:34.053 --> 26:35.853
- I'm throwing her. - Stop it.

26:36.283 --> 26:37.323
Let's do it.

26:38.293 --> 26:40.563
- Throw her or what? - Put her down.

26:40.692 --> 26:41.823
She's going to cry.

26:46.632 --> 26:47.932
That was mean. wasn't it?

26:52.172 --> 26:53.232
Happy birthday.

27:01.412 --> 27:03.783
Are you crazy? Why did you push her?

27:04.013 --> 27:05.482
Yoon Seo. are you okay?

27:07.182 --> 27:08.283
I'm okay.

27:08.283 --> 27:10.083
- Hurry up. I can't go. - You go.

27:10.083 --> 27:11.353
Go save her.

27:16.823 --> 27:17.863
Yoon Seo.

27:42.482 --> 27:43.482
Yoon Seo!

27:43.722 --> 27:46.422
- Help... - Do something!

27:49.023 --> 27:50.023
Darn it.

28:05.513 --> 28:07.412
Hurry up and help him.

28:12.253 --> 28:13.253
Are you okay?

28:14.323 --> 28:15.382
Yoon Seo!

28:16.222 --> 28:17.793
- Are you okay? - Help me carry her.

28:26.833 --> 28:28.533
I think we went too far.

28:28.932 --> 28:30.603
Will she be okay?

28:38.972 --> 28:40.783
Yoon Seo. are you okay?

28:41.613 --> 28:42.912
Are you in pain?

28:43.382 --> 28:45.452
- No. I'm okay. - Hold on.

28:55.023 --> 28:56.922
Why do you still look like that?

28:57.863 --> 28:59.192
You should've changed your clothes at least.

29:00.563 --> 29:02.303
I waited for you to wake up.

29:03.232 --> 29:05.003
Do you know how worried I was?

29:06.503 --> 29:07.642
I thought you were going to die.

29:08.642 --> 29:10.343
What happened?

29:11.043 --> 29:12.073
I don't know.

29:16.142 --> 29:17.182
What's this?

29:18.013 --> 29:19.083
Nothing.

29:22.353 --> 29:24.593
- Are you okay now? - What?

29:25.192 --> 29:28.392
You quit swimming because you couldn't enter water anymore.

29:29.763 --> 29:32.293
Let me go. Don't touch me.

29:32.632 --> 29:33.932
Seung Heon.

29:34.503 --> 29:36.103
Oh. about that...

29:37.732 --> 29:39.172
It's okay. I'm over it now.

29:40.533 --> 29:41.543
Really?

29:42.202 --> 29:44.543
I should gather everyone and talk to them.

29:44.642 --> 29:46.642
- Take some rest. - Okay.

30:00.152 --> 30:01.593
Apologize to Yoon Seo.

30:03.222 --> 30:04.333
Birthday noogies?

30:04.732 --> 30:07.632
Don't you think you took it too far?

30:08.763 --> 30:09.763
Sorry.

30:11.333 --> 30:12.833
We only...

30:13.902 --> 30:15.942
wanted to celebrate your birthday.

30:16.942 --> 30:19.672
It's okay. Don't cry.

30:21.283 --> 30:24.152
Really? Will you forgive me?

30:25.982 --> 30:26.982
Yes.

30:29.982 --> 30:31.422
I'm sorry. Yoon Seo.

30:32.093 --> 30:33.523
It's fine.

30:41.603 --> 30:43.932
- Go and check what's going on. - They will be here in a minute.

30:43.932 --> 30:45.132
They're back.

30:50.172 --> 30:51.972
Jun Hee. what now?

30:52.212 --> 30:54.942
We can't reach them. and we get no reception here.

30:55.813 --> 30:57.783
He's right. What are we going to do?

30:59.613 --> 31:02.083
Let's sleep in our rooms for now.

31:02.982 --> 31:04.692
I'll check again early in the morning tomorrow.

31:05.452 --> 31:06.452
Okay.

31:06.993 --> 31:08.293
Let's go.

31:12.962 --> 31:15.202
Guys. sleep in your rooms.

31:15.333 --> 31:16.533
Stop wasting your time here.

31:17.103 --> 31:18.732
Right. Go to sleep for now.

31:19.033 --> 31:20.972
Jun Hee and I will go check outside tomorrow.

31:21.343 --> 31:22.843
- Let's go to bed. - Go to your rooms.

31:22.843 --> 31:24.212
Yes. go to your rooms.

31:24.573 --> 31:26.773
Kim So Mi was faking it.

31:26.773 --> 31:28.743
Let it slide. She said sorry.

31:30.513 --> 31:32.313
She keeps doing that because you keep letting her get away.

31:33.583 --> 31:34.853
What can I do about it?

31:34.853 --> 31:36.523
Gosh. I hate that girl.

31:36.523 --> 31:38.692
You promised to play all night long.

31:38.692 --> 31:40.452
You still feel like playing after what happened?

31:40.652 --> 31:41.722
Just go to bed.

31:43.892 --> 31:46.263
A minute left to vote.

31:51.073 --> 31:52.073
What's this?

31:52.073 --> 31:54.142
(Remaining time)

31:58.172 --> 32:00.212
There's even an announcement.

32:00.573 --> 32:01.912
This is brilliant. Do you approve?

32:02.083 --> 32:03.912
Yes. but you made it.

32:03.912 --> 32:04.952
- No. - Hey. what is this?

32:04.952 --> 32:06.753
Did you see that?

32:06.753 --> 32:07.853
Isn't this brilliant?

32:08.882 --> 32:10.583
- He made it. - It wasn't me.

32:13.993 --> 32:15.023
Did you vote?

32:15.793 --> 32:17.392
- Yes. - Who did you vote for?

32:18.392 --> 32:19.432
Heo Yul?

32:21.962 --> 32:23.833
The voting has ended.

32:24.932 --> 32:27.172
I bet he got all the votes.

32:27.503 --> 32:29.472
You made this anyway.

32:29.472 --> 32:31.073
What did I do?

32:31.273 --> 32:33.573
Besides. why did you vote for me?

32:33.573 --> 32:34.912
Don't make this boring.

32:34.942 --> 32:37.043
See?

32:38.013 --> 32:42.652
Heo Yul with the most votes. 24 votes will be executed.

32:42.753 --> 32:44.892
- What? He got the most votes? - Bye.

32:51.763 --> 32:53.462
There he goes again.

32:56.103 --> 32:57.132
Cut it out.

32:59.732 --> 33:00.773
Are you acting again?

33:01.343 --> 33:02.472
It's boring. Stop it.

33:10.382 --> 33:11.412
What's going on?

33:11.652 --> 33:13.212
What's wrong?

33:19.622 --> 33:21.222
Hey. what's wrong?

33:21.722 --> 33:23.462
- What's wrong? - Are you okay?

33:23.493 --> 33:24.793
Is he okay?

33:24.793 --> 33:26.892
Yul. I said that's enough.

33:29.833 --> 33:30.902
What the...

33:34.003 --> 33:35.972
- What's going on? - Hey.

33:39.642 --> 33:40.982
What are you doing?

33:42.182 --> 33:44.083
- Stop it. - What are you doing?

33:44.083 --> 33:45.753
- What are you doing? - What's he doing?

33:46.853 --> 33:48.353
- Hey. - Stop.

33:49.353 --> 33:50.892
What on earth is your problem?

33:50.892 --> 33:52.652
- Yul. - Stop!

33:53.293 --> 33:55.093
That's enough.

33:55.462 --> 33:58.293
- What's wrong with him? - Somebody stop him.

33:58.763 --> 33:59.962
What are you doing?

34:03.062 --> 34:04.172
- Stop. - What was that for?

34:12.643 --> 34:13.973
- No. - Yul!

34:28.593 --> 34:29.623
Yul.

34:30.422 --> 34:32.593
What is wrong with Yul?

34:38.002 --> 34:40.232
- No! Oh. no! - Hey.

34:51.152 --> 34:54.113
Heo Yul was a Citizen.

34:56.082 --> 34:58.553
- What just happened? - What is going on?

35:50.602 --> 35:55.542
(Night Has Come)

